snippet.title: Johnny Depp trial: Ex-wife Amber Heard denies affairs
snippet.description:
The actor Amber Heard continued her evidence as she claimed she had been told Johnny Depp pushed his ex-girlfriend Kate Moss down some stairs while also denying an affair with co-star James Franco.

It's the eleventh day of Depp's libel action against the publishers of The Sun newspaper. The actor strongly denies any allegations of abuse.
